---
title: Chargrilled Pesto Lamb & Truffle Mayo Potatoes with Grilled Veggie Green Salad
description: This lamb shortloin is best cooked under the lid of a smokey barbecue. Paired with creamy truffle potatoes, a crisp rocket salad
and some nutty basil pesto for the lamb, this feast screams deluxe backyard dining from every angle. No barbie? No worries. Just follow our tips for cooking on the stove or in the oven!

*Keep an eye out... Due to sourcing challenges over the Christmas period, some of the fresh ingredients you receive may be slightly different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
